steps.html_instructions: Take the California 94 E/ML King Jr. Freeway ramp
Take the exit on the left onto CA-125 N

Keep left at the fork to stay on I-8 E
Entering Arizona
Keep right at the fork, follow signs for I-10 E/Phoenix and merge onto I-10 E
Take exit 147A-147B for AZ-202 Loop E/AZ-51 N
Keep right at the fork to continue on Exit 147A, follow signs for AZ-202 Loop E
Keep left to continue toward AZ-202 Loop E

Turn left onto AZ-87 N/N Country Club Dr
Continue to follow AZ-87 N

Turn right to merge onto I-40 E
Entering New Mexico
Take exit 159B-159C for I-25 N/I-25 S toward Santa Fe/Las Cruces
Keep left at the fork to continue on Exit 159C, follow signs for I-25 N/Santa Fe and merge onto I-25 N
Take exit 282A-282B for US-84 N/St Francis Dr toward US-285 N/Santa Fe Plaza
Continue onto US-285 N/US-84 W/S St Francis Dr
